{"tid":2219933,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"大批外傭在旺角道天橋聚集　部份無戴口罩","createTime":"2020-09-27T08:46:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-27T11:21:11.000Z","uid":20933,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"e8fdee086ba6d370e93200ce68ff99aa7dd7fcb4","tid":2219933,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T08:46:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://stream.881903.com/public/4f4f6e2d2e12fd7337d33ab337a15ebf/2020/09/cdf01d0fda5343c536f884a50b2a9caf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstream.881903.com%2Fpublic%2F4f4f6e2d2e12fd7337d33ab337a15ebf%2F2020%2F09%2Fcdf01d0fda5343c536f884a50b2a9caf.jpg&h=02df247f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://stream.881903.com/public/159cf6e78eb09b851d1609c2895c1325/2020/09/328204d9220a07adfd35ede2b095bc30.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstream.881903.com%2Fpublic%2F159cf6e78eb09b851d1609c2895c1325%2F2020%2F09%2F328204d9220a07adfd35ede2b095bc30.jpg&h=487ece73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不少外傭趁星期日休息日外出，在旺角道行人天橋，下午有大批外傭坐滿橋面兩邊聚餐聊天，有群組人數超過限聚令規定的最多4人，部份達10多人；不少人無戴口罩，有外傭就指會盡量在飲食期間才脫下口罩，不擔心感染。數名軍裝警員曾到場巡邏，未有發出勸喻或警告。 <br />\n<br />\n有外傭表示，僱主曾帶同她接受普及社區檢測，結果呈陰性，相信已經安全。有外傭就指，自己並無病徵，平時亦少外出，覺得並無參與病毒檢測的需要。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2359128\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2359128&d=31jm0GaxjznMjcF0xOQh0qb0OKgTvMyjK8k7SjVk7cc%3D&h=78beb77b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2359128</a>"},{"pid":"8d45cbad8c94162b398cac3b398e4cbf30a51fcd","tid":2219933,"uid":312363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T08:50:27.000Z","msg":"天橋群組<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"209ab56ec6b4df2dd8b1480036464541a46e5424","tid":2219933,"uid":184261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T08:51:43.000Z","msg":"賓印群組<img src=\"/assets/fac